ProcessWire Textile Textformatter module for ProcessWire 2.2+

Included are versions for multi-line trusted input (TextformatterTextile), 
for user-supplied multi-line input (TextformatterTextileRestricted) and for single-line, trusted, fields
(TextformatterTextileField.)

To install, copy these files (including subdirs) into /site/modules/TextformatterTextile/.

